article_title: Unique retail store helps people shop for health insurance
article_text:
Madison, WI (53711)

Today

Thunderstorms this morning, then partly cloudy during the afternoon hours. High near 85F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 80%..

Tonight

Partial cloudiness early, with scattered showers and thunderstorms overnight. Low 64F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 50%.

article_metadata.description: In May, Aaron and Melissa Becker opened a retail health insurance store in Middleton.
article_metadata.author: Steven Elbow | The Capital Times
